  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 14 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb9\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bcb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "14 people from United People's Power vote for Ranil Wickramasinghe - Minister Hareen Fernando",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Programs will be carried out under the leadership of the new President Ranil Wickremesinghe in order to lead the entire Parliament as a government. The new president has invited the main opposition party for that. So we will see whether the leader of the opposition will decide about the country or about the future elections, Minister Hareen Fernando said.",
        "The President said this while addressing the media at the Parliament premises after the completion of the poll.",
        "Ranil Wickresinghe's Courage is currently featured. However, this issue is very challenging. We believe that this will fulfill the great expectations of the people of Sri Lanka. The entire Parliament is expected to lead the government. We don't need posts at this time. We think they will do it right.",
        "For this you can travel along with Sajith Premadasa and others. Now there is an experienced leader. We believe that we can do the needful through him. Ranil Wickramasinghe's objective was an all-party government system. For that he called all the parties including the main opposition party. He especially called for United People's Power.",
        "So we will wait and see if the leader of the opposition Sajith Premadasa will think and act about the country now or will he act about the future elections. Also, 14 members of United People's Power have voted for Ranil Wickramasinghe in this election. Similarly 4 or 5 members have voted in TNA. He said that we had already expected this victory."
      ],
